 \frac{1}{\sqrt n - 1}
\frac{\sum_ {i=1}^{n} \frac{i}{n}}{n}\leq\frac{\sum_ {i=1}^{[\sqrt{n}]} \frac{i}{n}+\sum_ {i=[\sqrt n]+1}^{n}\frac{i}{n} }{n} \leq \frac{ [\sqrt {n }] \cdot  1+ (n-[\sqrt n])\frac{1}{ [\sqrt n]} } {n}\leq  
\frac{ \sqrt {n }+(n+1-\sqrt n)\frac{1}{ \sqrt n-1} } {n}= O(\sqrt n )\frac{1}{n}\rightarrow0
